%H A397043 Vaclav Kotesovec, <a href="/A397043/b397043.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000</a>
%F A397043 G.f.: Sum_{j>=1} (x^j/(1-x^j)) / Product_{k>=1} (1-x^k)^(k^2).
%F A397043 a(n) ~ A023871(n) * n^(1-p) * (log(n^(1-p)/(p*r)) + gamma) / (p*r), where p = 3/4 and r = 4*Pi / (3^(5/4) * 5^(1/4)).
%F A397043 a(n) ~ 15^(1/8) * exp(4*Pi*n^(3/4)/(3^(5/4)*5^(1/4)) - zeta(3)/(4*Pi^2)) * (log(15*n/Pi^4) + 4*gamma) / (Pi * 2^(7/2) * n^(3/8)), where gamma is the Euler-Mascheroni constant A001620.
%t A397043 nmax = 40; CoefficientList[Series[Sum[x^j/(1-x^j),{j,1,nmax}] / Product[(1-x^k)^(k^2), {k,1,nmax}], {x, 0, nmax}], x]
